<%- include("./partials/header"); -%>


<div class="container mt-5">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card text-center mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <button class="btn btn-warning btn-block" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#info1">
                        Solar Panel Basics
                    </button>
                    <div id="info1" class="collapse mt-3">
                        <img src="Img/casa-1.png" alt="Solar Panel Basics" class="img-fluid mb-2">
                        <p>Solar panels capture sunlight and convert it into electricity. They are an effective way to reduce your electricity bills and environmental footprint.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card text-center mb-3">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <button class="btn btn-warning btn-block" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#info2">
                        Benefits of Solar Panels
                    </button>
                    <div id="info2" class="collapse mt-3">
                        <img src="Img/casa-1.png" alt="Benefits of Solar Panels" class="img-fluid mb-2">
                        <p>Solar panels can significantly reduce electricity costs and provide a sustainable, renewable source of energy for over 25 years.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container mt-5" id="info">
    <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Information</h1>
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <img src="Img/casa-1.png" alt="casa" class="img-fluid rounded shadow-sm" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#solarModal" style="cursor: pointer;">
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="card-body bg-warning">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Save with Solar</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">Installing solar panels can help you save on electricity bills while reducing your carbon footprint.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card mb-3">
                <div class="card-body bg-success text-white">
                    <h2 class="card-title">Go Green</h2>
                    <p class="card-text">Solar energy is a renewable source of power, helping you contribute to a cleaner and greener environment.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="modal fade" id="solarModal" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-labelledby="solarModalLabel" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="modal-dialog" role="document">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h5 class="modal-title" id="solarModalLabel">About Solar Panels</h5>
                <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
                    <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
                </button>
            </div>
            <div class="modal-body">
                Solar panels convert sunlight into electricity, providing a sustainable and renewable energy source. They help reduce energy bills and have a lifespan of over 25 years. By installing solar panels, you can decrease your dependency on fossil fuels and contribute to environmental conservation.
            </div>
            <div class="modal-footer">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Close</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>






<%- include("partials/footer"); -%>